Class Diagnosis

java.lang.Object
org.CSPT.sc2001_grp1_proj1.entity.Diagnosis
public class Diagnosis extends Object
Represents a medical diagnosis given to a patient by a doctor. The diagnosis includes details such as the doctor's ID, the patient's ID, the diagnosis description, the treatment plan, the prescription, and the date and time of diagnosis.
